var camelCaseMap = HTML_ATTRIBUTES
  .concat(NON_STANDARD_ATTRIBUTES)
  .concat(SVG_ATTRIBUTES)
  .reduce(function (soFar, attr) {
    var lower = attr.toLowerCase();
    if (lower !== attr) {
      soFar[lower] = attr;
    }
    return soFar;
  }, {});
 
module.exports = camelCaseMap;
